---
title: Creamy Spiced Lentil and Paneer Curry with Sweet Potato and Spinach
description: Fragrant and gently spiced, Pasanda style seasoning is the perfect match for any rich and creamy curry. Made with spices common in Indian cuisine, this spice mix contains ingredients such as ground cumin, turmeric, cardamom and crushed black pepper.
